[YUKI]
Look at you sulking.

00:21:37.547 --> 00:21:40.300 position:50% align:center
Do you like it when
she worries about you?

00:21:41.634 --> 00:21:43.219 position:50% align:center
[TOHRU]
Oh, I almost forgot!

00:21:43.303 --> 00:21:46.264 position:50% align:center
There was another
really big change.

00:21:46.348 --> 00:21:48.558 position:50% align:center
